Interface GameCallbackCollection

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    SlotMachine
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SlotMachineImpl
    public interface GameCallbackCollection
    Supporting interface used in the Further Programming Assignment

    Provides methods for adding or removing a GameCallback from a Collection.

    Author:
    Ross Nye

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method Description
      int addCallback​(GameCallback callback)
      Adds a GameCallback; the callback is placed in a Collection.
      int removeCallback​(GameCallback callback)
      Removes supplied GameCallback from the Collection of registered callbacks.
